              <list>
                <item xml:id="addition1" n="1">
                  <ref target="#handNote2"/>
                  <p>At a comparatively recent period, the quires have been signed with letters from <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܝܕ</foreign> to <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܟ</foreign>.</p>
                </item>
                <item xml:id="addition2" n="2">
                  <locus from="1a" to="1a"/>
                  <ref target="#handNote3"/>
                  <p>On fol. 1 a there is a note, stating that this was one of the 250 volumes, brought to the <placeName>convent of <persName>S. Mary Deipara</persName></placeName> by the abbat <persName>Moses of Nisibis</persName>, <date when-custom="1243" datingMethod="Seleucid">A. Gr. 1243</date>,  <date when="0932" calendar="Gregorian">A.D. 932</date>.</p>
                </item>
              </list>
